BTTAdditionalActions.BTTInlineAppleScript: tell application "Brave Browser"	set windows_list to every window	repeat with w in windows_list		set tabs_list to every tab in w		repeat with t in tabs_list			if URL of t starts with "https://meet.google.com" then				tell application "Brave Browser"					set get_status to execute t javascript "var el = document.querySelector('.VfPpkd-Bz112c-LgbsSe.yHy1rc.eT1oJ.tWDL4c.uaILN.bPEdgb.qIiG8c').nextSibling.innerText; if(el.includes('Turn on microphone')) { true } else { false } "					set status to ((get_status) as string)					if (status is "true") then						execute t javascript "var el = document.querySelector('.VfPpkd-Bz112c-LgbsSe.yHy1rc.eT1oJ.tWDL4c.uaILN.bPEdgb.qIiG8c.FTMc0c.N2RpBe.jY9Dbb');el.click();"						return "Mute"					else if (status is "false") then						execute t javascript "var el = document.querySelector('.VfPpkd-Bz112c-LgbsSe.yHy1rc.eT1oJ.tWDL4c.uaILN.bPEdgb.qIiG8c.HNeRed');el.click();"						return "Unmute"					else						return ""					end if				end tell			end if		end repeat	end repeatend tell
